      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、完売です！\n売り切りましたーっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ it's sold out!\nWe sold out completely!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.580408001
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いや、完売は嬉しいんだけど\n怜には別の目的があるだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ being sold out is great and all\nBut Rei‚ don't you have another purpose?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.1137411913
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "わ、分かってますけどっ！\nスーパータケミヤ時代を思い出しちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I know that!\nIt just reminded me of my time at Super Takemiya…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.7137411913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか懐かしいな……\nけどライブまで時間がない、急いで着替えてみてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It feels nostalgic…\nBut there's not much time until the live‚ hurry and change.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "……うっ、ちょっと怖いです\n{user}さん……大丈夫ですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ugh‚ I'm a little scared.\n{user}-san… Are you sure about this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、努力は報われるよ\n……でもなぁ、なんせ短時間だからな……どうかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ your hard work will pay off.\n…But well‚ it's a short time‚ so I don't know…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんな不安になること言わないで下さいよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't say things that make me anxious…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……多分、大丈夫だと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I think you'll be fine‚ probably.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "多分って言わないで下さい！\nほら、見て下さい！　引っ込んでますよね！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't say \"probably\"!\nLook‚ it's sticking out‚ isn't it!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "こらこら！　怜、落ち着け！\nこんな所でお腹を出そうとするんじゃない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ hey! Rei‚ calm down!\nDon't try to show off your stomach in a place like this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、あまりに不安で取り乱しました……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry‚ I got so anxious and lost control…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "やるだけやったんだ、後は祈ろう\nさぁ、着替えてきてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You've done all you can‚ now let's hope for the best.\nNow‚ go and change.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "はい、行ってきます……\n必ず、着てみせますから……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I'll be right back…\nI'll definitely show it off…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
